highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “DtMF” is the highest at #3.
“Round and Round” by Lee Soo-In, Jeong Geun, and North is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #1.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 141 days straight.
